{"id":783,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":783,"title":"Jeremiah 14","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 14"],[".studySummary",["i","Jeremiah prays because of dearth and famine—The Lord will not hear because of the wickedness of His people."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.1","order":"02.25.014.51722"},["b","1"],"The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that came to Jeremiah concerning the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"dearth"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.2","order":"02.25.014.51723"},["b","2"],"Judah mourneth, and the gates thereof languish; they are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"black unto the ground"],"; and the cry of Jerusalem is gone up."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.3","order":"02.25.014.51724"},["b","3"],"And their nobles have sent their little ones to the waters: they came to the pits,",["i","and"],"found no water; they returned with their vessels empty; they were ashamed and confounded, and covered their heads."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.4","order":"02.25.014.51725"},["b","4"],"Because the ground is chapt, for there was no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"rain"],"in the earth, the plowmen were ashamed, they covered their heads."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.5","order":"02.25.014.51726"},["b","5"],"Yea, the hind also calved in the field, and forsook",["i","it,"],"because there was no grass."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.6","order":"02.25.014.51727"},["b","6"],"And the wild asses did stand in the high places, they snuffed up the wind like",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"dragons"],"; their eyes did fail, because",["i","there was"],"no grass."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.7","order":"02.25.014.51728"},["b","7"],"¶O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", though our iniquities testify against us, do thou",["i","it"],"for thy name’s sake: for our backslidings are many; we have sinned against thee."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.8","order":"02.25.014.51729"},["b","8"],"O the hope of Israel, the saviour thereof in time of trouble, why shouldest thou be as a stranger in the land, and as a wayfaring man",["i","that"],"turneth aside to tarry for a night?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.9","order":"02.25.014.51730"},["b","9"],"Why shouldest thou be as a man astonied, as a mighty man",["i","that"],"cannot save? yet thou, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","art"],"in the midst of us, and we are called by thy name; leave us not."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.10","order":"02.25.014.51731"},["b","10"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto this people, Thus have they loved to wander, they have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"refrained"],"their feet, therefore the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"doth not accept them; he will now remember their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"iniquity"],", and visit their sins."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.11","order":"02.25.014.51732"},["b","11"],"Then said the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto me,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Pray"],"not for this people for",["i","their"],"good."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.12","order":"02.25.014.51733"},["b","12"],"When they fast, I will not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"hear"],"their cry; and when they offer burnt offering and an oblation, I will not accept them: but I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"consume"],"them by the sword, and by the famine, and by the pestilence."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.13","order":"02.25.014.51734"},["b","13"],"¶Then said I, Ah, Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"! behold, the prophets say unto them, Ye shall not see the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sword"],", neither shall ye have famine; but I will give you assured peace in this place."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.14","order":"02.25.014.51735"},["b","14"],"Then the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto me, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"prophets"],"prophesy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"lies"],"in my name: I sent them not, neither have I commanded them, neither spake unto them: they prophesy unto you a false",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"vision"],"and divination, and a thing of nought, and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"deceit"],"of their heart."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.15","order":"02.25.014.51736"},["b","15"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"concerning the prophets that prophesy in my name, and I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"sent"],"them not, yet they say, Sword and famine shall not be in this land; By sword and famine shall those prophets be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"consumed"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.16","order":"02.25.014.51737"},["b","16"],"And the people to whom they prophesy shall be cast out in the streets of Jerusalem because of the famine and the sword; and they shall have none to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"bury"],"them, them, their wives, nor their sons, nor their daughters: for I will pour their wickedness upon them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.17","order":"02.25.014.51738"},["b","17"],"¶Therefore thou shalt say this word unto them; Let mine eyes run down with tears night and day, and let them not cease: for the virgin daughter of my people is broken with a great breach, with a very grievous blow."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.18","order":"02.25.014.51739"},["b","18"],"If I go forth into the field, then behold the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"slain"],"with the sword! and if I enter into the city, then behold them that are sick with famine! yea, both the prophet and the priest go about into a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"land"],"that they know not."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.19","order":"02.25.014.51740"},["b","19"],"Hast thou utterly rejected Judah? hath thy soul lothed Zion? why hast thou smitten us, and",["i","there is"],"no healing for us? we looked for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"peace"],", and",["i","there is"],"no good; and for the time of healing, and behold trouble!"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.20","order":"02.25.014.51741"},["b","20"],"We",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"acknowledge"],", O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", our wickedness,",["i","and"],"the iniquity of our fathers: for we have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"sinned"],"against thee."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.21","order":"02.25.014.51742"},["b","21"],"Do not abhor",["i","us,"],"for thy name’s sake, do not disgrace the throne of thy glory: remember, break not thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"covenant"],"with us."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.22","order":"02.25.014.51743"},["b","22"],"Are there",["i","any"],"among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"vanities of the Gentiles"],"that can cause rain? or can the heavens give",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"showers"],"?",["i","art"],"not thou he, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God? therefore we will wait upon thee: for thou hast",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"made"],"all these",["i","things."]]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.1a","order":"02.25.014.51744"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/famine"},"TG Famine"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.2a","order":"02.25.014.51746"},["b","2a"],["span.small","OR"],"dejected."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.4a","order":"02.25.014.51748"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/3.3"},"Jer. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.6a","order":"02.25.014.51750"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"jackals."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.10a","order":"02.25.014.51752"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abstain"},"TG Abstain"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-mastery"},"Self-Mastery"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.10b","order":"02.25.014.51754"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.11a","order":"02.25.014.51756"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.16"},"Jer. 7:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.14"},"11:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.12a","order":"02.25.014.51758"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.24.23-25"},"Mosiah 11:24 (23–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/21.15"},"21:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.7.6-8"},"D&C 101:7 (6–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.12b","order":"02.25.014.51760"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/16.4"},"Jer. 16:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.13a","order":"02.25.014.51762"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.12"},"Jer. 5:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.14a","order":"02.25.014.51764"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"TG False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.14b","order":"02.25.014.51766"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/27.10"},"Jer. 27:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-doctrine"},"TG False Doctrine"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.14c","order":"02.25.014.51768"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.14d","order":"02.25.014.51770"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deceit"},"TG Deceit"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.15a","order":"02.25.014.51772"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/authority"},"TG Authority"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.15b","order":"02.25.014.51774"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.12"},"Jer. 44:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.16a","order":"02.25.014.51776"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/79.3"},"Ps. 79:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.18a","order":"02.25.014.51778"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.21"},"Lam. 2:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.18b","order":"02.25.014.51780"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.19a","order":"02.25.014.51782"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/8.15"},"Jer. 8:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.20a","order":"02.25.014.51784"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/confession"},"TG Confession"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.20b","order":"02.25.014.51786"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.6"},"Ps. 106:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.21a","order":"02.25.014.51788"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.45"},"Ps. 106:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.22a","order":"02.25.014.51790"},["b","22a"],["span.small","IE"],"worthless idols of the nations."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.22b","order":"02.25.014.51792"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/3.3.1-5"},"Jer. 3:3 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.22c","order":"02.25.014.51794"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.2"},"Mosiah 4:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/9.15"},"3 Ne. 9:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.9"},"D&C 14:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.1"},"45:1"],"."]]}
